'''Gero Merhart von Bernegg''' (17 October 1886 – 4 March 1959) was a German archaeologist. Although he worked at the same time when German nationalism and [[Nazi archaeology]] was dominant in Germany, he was not a "Nazi archaeologist".  He came into conflict with [[Hans Reinerth]].

